#The vocabulary questions is going to measure your vocabulary proficiency it is important to know if you recoginize important words in a passage.


#RECOGINIZING VOCABULARY QUESTIONS

*Words highlighet in the reading passages.

*You'll see Phrases Like "Closest in the meaning to", "the author means".






#ABOUT THE VOCABULARY TO BE MEASURED

Note that the vocabylary focused on the TOEFL EBT is the ACADEMYC vocabulary, there's no way to be prepared to the vocabulary test without really expending it, and reading a lot of academic papers.

There's a difference between Academic vocabulary and Specialized Vocabulary.



#TIP FOR INCREASING VOCABULARY.

*Many english words come from latin or greek so if you study latin and greek roots you can doind well.
